.Sh COMMANDS
.\" ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Cm help Oo Fl l Oc Op Ar command_name
.Pp
Prints usage for all available commands.
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl l , Fl -list-commands
List command usages only, without parameter explanation.
.It Ar command_name
Prints usage for the specified command.
.El
